kind%20of%20space%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsundar-pichai-google-ai-beat-by-openai-chatgpt-launch-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECEO%20Sundar%20Pichai%3C%2Fa%3E%20announced%20Project%20Suncatcher%2C%20a%20%26quot%3Bresearch%20moonshot%26quot%3B%20that%20would%20deploy%20satellites%20equipped%20with%20Google's%20custom%20Tensor%20Processing%20Units%2C%20which%20already%20power%20many%20of%20Google's%20AI%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInspired%20by%20our%20history%20of%20moonshots%2C%20from%20quantum%20computing%20to%20autonomous%20driving%2C%26quot%3B%20Pichar%20wrote%20on%20X%2C%20%26quot%3BProject%20Suncatcher%20is%20exploring%20how%20we%20could%20one%20day%20build%20scalable%20ML%20compute%20systems%20in%20space%2C%20harnessing%20more%20of%20the%20sun's%20power.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPichar%20added%20that%20the%20sun%20emits%20more%20power%20than%20100%20trillion%20times%20humanity's%20total%20electricity%20production%2C%20and%20that%20Google%20plans%20to%20launch%20two%20prototype%20satellites%20in%20early%202027%2C%20each%20carrying%20Trillium-generation%20TPUs%20to%20test%20their%20performance%20in%20low-Earth%20orbit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-appears-to-have-shunned-nvidia-chips-for-google-ai-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETPU%20chips%3C%2Fa%3E%20withstood%20radiation%20simulations%20in%20a%20particle%20accelerator%2C%20Google%20still%20faces%20hurdles%20ahead.%20According%20to%20Google's%20research%20paper%2C%20which%20Pichai%20posted%20in%20a%20thread%2C%20the%20final%20product%20would%20involve%20fleets%20of%20solar-powered%20satellites%20connected%20by%20optical%20links%20to%20exchange%20data%2C%20said%20the%20paper.%20Pichai%20said%20in%20the%20X%20post%20that%20thermal%20management%20and%20reliability%20are%20both%20challenging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20tech%20giant%20could%20pu