part%2C%20has%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbillionaires-shouldnt-exist-zohran-mamdani-new-york-wealth-inequality-poverty-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebillionaires%20should%20not%20exist%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECuomo%20also%20won%20the%20support%20of%20two%20other%20major%20billionaires%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20election%3A%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20Elon%20Musk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhether%20you%20personally%20like%20Andrew%20Cuomo%20or%20not%2C%20you%20really%20have%20no%20choice%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20wrote%20on%20Truth%20Social%20on%20Monday%20night.%20%26quot%3BYou%20must%20vote%20for%20him%2C%20and%20hope%20he%20does%20a%20fantastic%20job.%20He%20is%20capable%20of%20it%2C%20Mamdani%20is%20not!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBear%20in%20mind%20that%20a%20vote%20for%20Curtis%20is%20really%20a%20vote%20for%20Mumdumi%20or%20whatever%20his%20name%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20wrote%20on%20X.%20%26quot%3BVOTE%20CUOMO!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20support%20wasn't%20enough%20to%20counter%20the%20growing%20momentum%20behind%20Mamdani.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e3749ef1-1749-4226-91ad-1ea069b9044a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20battle%20over%20the%20business%20of%20New%20York%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20critiques%20of%20Mamdani%20from%20the%20billionaire%20class%20revolve%20around%20the%20future%20of%20New%20York%20as%20a%20business%20hub.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20fund%20his%20ambitious%20platform%2C%20Mamdani%20has%20proposed%20raising%20the%20corporate%20tax%20rate%20and%20increasing%20the%20income%20tax%20on%20millionaires%20by%20two%20percentage%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20result%2C%20some%20of%20Mamdani's%20wealthy%20antagonists%20have%20said%2C%20will%20be%20an%20exodus%20from%20New%20York%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20both%20businesses%20and%20high%20earners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThink%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fken-griff