f%20you%20want%20to%20do%20something%20different%2C%20like%20build%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-agi-artificial-general-intelligence-explained-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epersonal%20AGI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20that%20might%20not%20fit%20with%20their%20advertising%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20dawned%20on%20me%20that%20I%20needed%20to%20chart%20a%20path%20to%20pursue%20my%20interest%20in%20robotics.%20A%20startup%20would%20allow%20me%20to%20iterate%20fast%2C%20take%20risks%2C%20and%20be%20nimble.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f292e747-3f4c-4cb3-acd0-ff4b7c9ee379%5C%22%3EMoving%20to%20Japan%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20final%20year%20at%20Google%2C%20I%20persuaded%20my%20manager%20to%20send%20me%20to%20Google's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-from-us-to-tokyo-japan-better-quality-of-life-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETokyo%20office%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%20was%20in%202020%2C%20and%20I%20spent%20a%20year%20there%20before%20I%20left%20to%20launch%20Integral%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhy%20Japan%3F%20That%20goes%20back%20to%20my%20interest%20and%20passion%20for%20applying%20AI%20to%20robotics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20the%20bulk%20of%20my%20career%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fin-silicon-valley-it-is-the-summer-of-fomo-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESilicon%20Valley%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20I%20saw%20firsthand%20that%20the%20US%20is%20a%20world%20leader%20in%20AI.%20The%20US%2C%20however%2C%20isn't%20as%20strong%20in%20robotics.%20That's%20partly%20because%20it%20has%20been%20outsourcing%20manufacturing%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJapan%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20is%20the%20world%20leader%20in%20robotics.%20It%20makes%20most%20of%20the%20world's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fartificial-intelligence-robotics-predictive-maintenance-manufacturing-factory-solutions-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eindustrial%20robots%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Going%20to%20Japan%20allowed%20me%20to%20combine%20the%20best%20of%20AI%20from%20Silicon%20Valley%20with%20the%20best%20of%20robotics%20in%20Tokyo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoing%20to%20Japan%20gave%20me%20access%20to%20the%20country's%20huge%20robotics%20ecosystem.%20There%20are%20so%20many%20players%20in%20robotics%2C%20ranging%20from%20suppliers%20to%20manufacturers%20to%20end%20customers.%20You%20need%20to%20understand%20the%20ecosystem%20if%20you%20want%20to%20serve%20the%20market%20effectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20fortunate%20to%20spend%20my%20final%20year%20at%20Google%20in%20Japan.%20I%20used%20it%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20immerse%20myself%20in%20the%20language%20and%20culture.%20To%20become%20conversant%20in%20Japanese%2C%20I%20placed%20myself%20in%20uncomfortable%20situations%20where%20I%20had%20to%20communicate%20with%20locals.%20Today%2C%20I%20feel%20comfortable%20talking%20to%20people%20I%20meet%20on%20the%20street.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20leaving%20Google%2C%20I%20founded%20Integral%20AI%20in%202021.%20My%20company's%20goal%20is%20to%20build%20an%20AI%20that%20can%20control%20robots%20and%20autonomous%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223b892e27-9fcd-48f9-8986-1b1910f9365c%5C%22%3EGetting%20the%20best%20of%20both%20worlds%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERunning%20my%20business%20in%20Japan%20does%20come%20with%20pros%20and%20cons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20that%20took%20getting%20used%20to%20was%20Japan's%20rigid%20system%20of%20rules%20and%20administrative%20procedures%2C%20which%20can%20be%20old-school%20and%20inflexible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20you%20must%20use%20a%20personal%20seal%2C%20or%20what%20the%20Japanese%20call%20a%20%26quot%3Bhanko%2C%26quot%3B%20to%20sign%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20the%20way%20documents%20are%20handled.%20It%20took%20me%20three%20months%20to%20open%20my%20company's%20bank%20account%2C%20despite%20having%20a%20Japanese%20in