day.%20He%20also%20said%20CoCounsel%20adoption%20is%20outpacing%20rivals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ce3a4cfc-1e40-424a-b02f-076cf5a3bd24%5C%22%3EA%20CoCounsel%20moat%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CEO%20framed%20Thomson%20Reuters'%20moat%20as%20a%20powerful%20combination%20of%20its%20Westlaw%20legal%20data%20and%20human-in-the-loop%20editing%20and%20validation%2C%20arguing%20this%20is%20essential%20in%20an%20industry%20where%20accuracy%2C%20timeliness%2C%20and%20security%20are%20paramount.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLitigation%20is%20high-stakes%20work%20with%20no%20room%20for%20error%20and%20significant%20consequences%20for%20being%20wrong%2C%26quot%3B%20Hasker%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20Westlaw%20product%20ingests%20more%20than%20300%20million%20documents%20a%20year%20from%20hundreds%20of%20court%20systems%20and%20tens%20of%20millions%20of%20rulings.%20An%20in-house%20bench%20of%20attorneys%20and%20editors%20turns%20this%20scramble%20of%20data%20into%20court-safe%20guidance%2C%20writing%20headnotes%2C%20verifying%20facts%2C%20and%20tagging%20issues%20to%20make%20the%20content%20easier%20to%20find.%20Roughly%2085%25%20of%20primary%20documents%20in%20Westlaw%2C%20such%20as%20cases%20and%20statutes%2C%20carry%20these%20editorial%20upgrades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20strategy%20now%20is%20to%20push%20beyond%20retrieval%20and%20summarization%20and%20into%20more%20generative%20services%20that%20help%20lawyers%20with%20more%20valuable%20tasks.%20That%20includes%20agentic%20workflows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2250523b24-bdd8-4378-8ad2-d522231ac2b7%5C%22%3EThe%20OpenAI%20question%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20hanging%20over%20everyone%20in%20legal%20tech%2C%20Thomson%20Reuters%20included%2C%20is%20whether%20OpenAI%20jumps%20in.%20This%20AI%20giant%20could%20sell%20a%20vertically%20packaged%20app%20to%20law%20firms%20and%20in-house%20teams%2C%20though%20there%20are%20no%20clear%20signs%20this%20is%20in%20the%20cards%20right%20now.%20Still%2C%20fears%20flared%